if QuestManager.is_quest_in_progress("talk_to_perkins") == true:
	perkins: This dialogue shows if you're currently on the "talk to Perkins" quest.
	perkins: Because the condition for completing the quest is talking to me, you've just completed it.
	perkins: That means the next time you talk to me will be will be my default dialogue.
	You feel that you now understand Dialogic a little better.
	[signal arg="objective_completed:talk_to_perkins:talk_to_perkins_objective"]
else:
	perkins: Now you're talking to me outside the quest.